dct_title_s: Map Showing Assessed Valuations of Properties Fronting on Arthur Kills in New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Raritan Bay to Newark Bay along Arthur Kills.
Map depicts the names of the various property owners as well as a chart showing the acreage and price values of the various properties.
